释义：
take the opportunity 抓住机会
与前面的句型有点差异，take the opportunity 表示“得到……的机会”，尤其在表达“借机做某事”的时候经常会用到 I'll take the opportunity to ...
例句：
I'm happy I'm able to give you this opportunity.
我很高兴能为你提供这次机会。
I'd like to take this opportunity to say I'm getting married next month.
我想借此机会跟你说，我下个月要结婚了。
You may not get an opportunity to do that research.
你可能没机会做那个研究了。
You can take this opportunity to get to know her well.
你可以借此机会多了解了解她。
对话：
A: Randy has a chance to start his own business.
兰迪有机会开创他自己的事业。
B: I hope he takes the opportunity. He might get rich.
我希望他能抓住机会，他很有可能会变成富翁的。